data.description: Beautiful 4 BR, 2.5BA, 3 Gar family home in the Royalwood neighborhood in Fishers. Home features vaulted ceilings with a spacious open floorplan & great kitchen offering stainless steel appliances. LVP flooring provides a nice clean look. Extra family den area provides an added bonus rm great for an office. The 2nd floor has a spacious loft & 4 BR's. One of which is the master suite with tray ceiling & spacious bath room. Backyard is fenced nicely for children & the deck is great for cookouts & entertaining. Also has comfortable front porch for relaxing as well.
